<doc id="558261" wikidata="Q5694875" url="?curid=558261" title="Heavenly Handel">
<text>Heavenly Handel: Arias and Duets is the title of a music recording Virgin Classics released on two compact discs in early 2004. It is a performance of arias and duets from operas by Georg Friedrich Händel.

The Virgin Classics catalog number for &quot;Heavenly Handel&quot; is 5624002.

== Track listing ==

The following list shows the tracks of this recording.

=== First compact disc ===
